		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV></DIV><FONT color=#99ff00><FONT color=#ffffff></FONT><FONT color=#ffffff></FONT><FONT color=#ffffff></FONT><FONT color=#ffffff></FONT><FONT color=#ffffff></FONT>CLASS:</FONT><FONT color=#ccff00> </FONT><FONT color=#cc0000>MONK</FONT>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00>HP: <FONT color=#ffffff>High</FONT><BR>Mana: <FONT color=#ffffff>N/A</FONT><BR>Endurance: <FONT color=#ffffff>Low</FONT><BR>AC: </FONT><FONT color=#ffffff>High</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00>HP Regen: <FONT color=#ffffff>Not Important</FONT><BR>Mana Regen: <FONT color=#ffffff>N/A</FONT><BR>Endurance Regen: </FONT><FONT color=#ffffff>Very Important (High)</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00>Strength: <FONT color=#ffffff>Not Important</FONT><BR>Stamina: <FONT color=#ffffff>Not Important</FONT><BR>Agility: <FONT color=#ffffff>Not Important</FONT><FONT color=#99ff00></FONT><BR>Dexterity: <FONT color=#ffffff>Not Important</FONT><BR>Charisma: <FONT color=#ffffff>Not Important</FONT><BR>Intelligence: <FONT color=#ffffff>Not Important</FONT><BR>Wisdom: </FONT><FONT color=#ffffff>Not Important</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00>Cold Resist: <FONT color=#ffffff>Important (low)</FONT><BR>Disease Resist: <FONT color=#ffffff>Important (low)<BR></FONT>Poison Resist: <FONT color=#ffffff>Important (low)</FONT><BR>Magic Resist: <FONT color=#ffffff>Important (High)<BR></FONT>Fire Resist: </FONT><FONT color=#ffffff>Important (low)<BR></FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00>Attack:<FONT color=#ffffff> Important (medium)<BR></FONT>Delay: <FONT color=#ffffff>Important (medium)</FONT><BR>Damage: <FONT color=#ffffff>Important (high)<BR></FONT>Range:<FONT color=#ffffff> Important (medium)</FONT><BR></FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00>Haste: </FONT><FONT color=#ffffff>Important (low)<BR></FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00>Combat Effects: <FONT color=#ffffff>Not Important</FONT><BR>Shielding: <FONT color=#ffffff>Important (Medium)</FONT><BR>Stun Resist: <FONT color=#ffffff>Important (Low)</FONT><BR>Strikethrough: <FONT color=#ffffff>Important (Medium)</FONT><BR>Spell Shield: <FONT color=#ffffff>Important (Low)<BR></FONT>Avoidance: </FONT><FONT color=#ffffff>Important (medium)</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00>Accuracy:&nbsp;<FONT color=#ffffff> Priority (Medium)</FONT><BR>DOT Shielding: </FONT><FONT color=#ffffff>Priority (High)</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#99ff00>Skill Mods: <FONT color=#ffffff>Priority</FONT> <FONT color=#ffffff>(High)</FONT><BR>Click Effects: <FONT color=#ffffff>Important (Low)</FONT><BR>Proc Effects: <FONT color=#ffffff>Backburner</FONT><BR>Worn Effects: <FONT color=#ffffff>Backburner</FONT><BR>Focus Effects:</FONT> <FONT color=#ffffff>Important (Low)</FONT><BR></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>HP </FONT>- Valuable. When choosing Gear, I always keep this in consideration.</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>AC</FONT> - Valuable.</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Endurance</FONT> - Valuable.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Health Regen</FONT> - I dont consider this at all when i choose gear.</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Endurance Regen</FONT> -&nbsp;I'm an Innerflame fiend. I burn it when I want to which is quite often.</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#ffffff></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#ffffff><FONT color=#cc00cc>Melee Stats</FONT> seem to MAX out pretty easily. 'Nuff Said.</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#ffffff><FONT color=#cc00cc>Svs</FONT> - Like to see More MR. Even with Resist Buffs, MAGIC SV seem to be hard to get MAX'd Out.</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#ffffff></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#ffffff><FONT color=#cc00cc>ATK</FONT> - I'd like to MAX but from what I understand, It WILL come with Gear</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#ffffff><FONT color=#cc00cc>DMG/DLY</FONT> - Valuable.</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#ffffff><FONT color=#cc00cc>Range</FONT> - Valuable. Like to see a more variety of 200+ rng items for those monks without Ton Po's Mystical Pouch and starfishies.</FONT></DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#ffffff><FONT color=#cc00cc>Haste</FONT> - Valuable.</FONT></DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Combat Effects</FONT> - Nice to have but really dont care if gear has this or not.</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Shielding</FONT> - Valuable. Rarely do i see Shielding items for monks &amp; the other leather users. I jump on the chance whenever I can get gear with some Reservation. IF the HPs are&nbsp;upgrading me nicely and My avoidance stays MAX, then I will try to win some 4% and higher shielding gear.</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Stun Resist</FONT> - Useful to have but not really a consideration for me. Rather pass it to a caster that can heal me when i need it.</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Strikethroug</FONT><FONT color=#cc00cc>h</FONT> - Useful. rarely see it fire off though for me.</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Spell Shield</FONT> - Nice to have but IF i really need to completely avoid that Stun/snare for a couple seconds for a pull, I'm Dreamwalking that mob to group/raid.</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Avoidance</FONT> - Valuable. Leather easily MAX OUT this&nbsp;and Some later on. Its Safe to say I can stay MAXed and focus on gaining other gear with some type of shielding or Skill mods.</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Accuracy</FONT> - Valuable. Important have. I am currently working on raising&nbsp;it. From what i understand, its easy to do from what higher geared monks say... I say its easier said than done =p</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>DOT Shielding</FONT> - Very Important. I'm working on it...</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Skill Mods</FONT> - Very Important. I havent looked too far ahead of whats to come but I try to keep my Avoidance at its highest potential. Its Very Noticeble when MAX Avoid AAs, Improve Dodge, Dodge 8%, Improved Block, Block 8% all come together. I think Very heavily about losing either of these. I dont crunch numbers to validate any of this but i notice it to the point where I weigh these mods over Hps. I have passed over 200hp+ upgrades because of it and so far, I dont regret it...</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Clicky Effects</FONT> - Nice to have. Its more taking care of yourself when you dont have the class to buff you and need junk buffs.</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Proc Effects/Worn Effects</FONT>&nbsp;- Useful but&nbsp;these on the backburner for me. I'll just use my personal tribute if i really, really needed it.</DIV>
<DIV><FONT color=#cc00cc>Focus effect</FONT> - Important. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV><BR></DIV>	
		</td></tr>
