		<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	
		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV>
<DIV>Class ranger</DIV>
<DIV>Progession: above Qvic, below Anguish</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>HP:&nbsp; Very Important<BR>Mana:&nbsp; Important especially when soloing in raids I normally have plenty, unless I am only healer in group</DIV>
<DIV>Endurance: Not important unless we get a disc that really uses alot of it<BR>AC: important</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>HP Regen: Important Nice to have to cut down on down time</DIV>
<DIV>Mana Regen: some what important depending on the situation we are in<BR>Endurance Regen: no need</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Strength: Important, I find alot of items little short on<BR>Stamina: Important, yet my sta is way way past max<BR>Agility: little important<BR>Dexterity: little important, another easy max area<BR>Charisma: only needed for selling and buying<BR>Intelligence: no need<BR>Wisdom: Important for mana but Way too much out there</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>All resists important yet I find myself low in PR and FR then DR around middle</DIV>
<DIV>Cold Resist: plenty out there<BR>Disease Resist: Mid<BR>Poison Resist: Low<BR>Magic Resist: plenty out there<BR>Fire Resist: Low</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Attack: Important good amount out there<BR>Damage: Important</DIV>
<DIV>Other: I still get too much argo even through melee, almost need a disc jolt instead of a spell with a cast time for quicker jolts</DIV>
<DIV><BR>Range: range dps is&nbsp;little important unless using trueshot, nowadays melee is better dps</DIV>
<DIV>Haste: very Important</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Combat Effects: not really important<BR>Shielding: very important<BR>Stun Resist: not really important<BR>Strikethrough: important for dps only</DIV>
<DIV>Spell Shield: very important<BR>Avoidance: very important<BR>Accuracy:&nbsp;important<BR>DOT Shielding: important</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Skill Mods: useless<BR>Click Effects: nice to have</DIV>
<DIV>Proc Effects: love the lifetap augs</DIV>
<DIV>Worn Effects: Not many of these left that are not some kind of focus effect<BR>Focus Effects: very Important<BR></DIV></DIV>
								<p><div style="width: 100%; height: 120; overflow: hidden;">
								
							<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=446119">Tadenea the Quester</a><br>75 Huntmaster<br>Test Server
