		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		" 
			>
			<DIV></DIV><BR>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>

<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>-------<BR>CLASS: BARD</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>HP: <BR>Mana: <BR>Endurance: <BR>AC: </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>HP Regen: <BR>Mana Regen: <BR>Endurance Regen: </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Strength: <BR>Stamina: <BR>Agility: <BR>Dexterity: <BR>Charisma: <BR>Intelligence: <BR>Wisdom: </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Cold Resist: <BR>Disease Resist: <BR>Poison Resist: <BR>Magic Resist: <BR>Fire Resist: </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Attack: <BR>Delay: <BR>Damage: <BR>Range: </DIV>
<DIV>Haste: </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Combat Effects: <BR>Shielding: <BR>Stun Resist: <BR>Strikethrough: <BR>Spell Shield: <BR>Avoidance: <BR>Accuracy: <BR>DOT Shielding: </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Skill Mods: <BR>Click Effects: <BR>Proc Effects: <BR>Worn Effects: <BR>Focus Effects: <BR><U>INSTRUMENT MODIFIERS:</U></DIV>
<DIV>-------</DIV><BR>
<HR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<P>Dear Merloc,</P>
<P>In your list of stats you for got one very important stat: <U>instrument modifiers.</U><BR>While I am aware that this is a stat only applying to one class, I couldn't help but notice you completely forgot about these modifiers, which are the core of our class. Hopefully I have brought your attention to <U>the instrument modifiers,</U> so that you can start by doing&nbsp;a beter job in this field.</P>
<P>For more details, you can check the bard boards, I am sure you can find all the feedback you need in the numerous threads containing over 2 years of frustration.</P>
<P>&nbsp;</P>
<P>Kind regards<BR></P>	
